dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Plieto [sic] Hills/ South 1/2 of Coal Oil Canyon quadrangles, Kern County, California
dct_alternative_sm: Pleito Hills and Coal Oil Canyon map
Geology Pleito Hills and Coal Oil Canyon quadrangles
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.

"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle PLEITO HILLS, CA 1995, NIMA 2153 I NE -- Series V895; COAL OIL CANYON, CA 1955, AMS 2154 II SE -- Series V895; photorevised 1968 and 1973."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
